gainst systematic order flow imbalances and resulting mispricings in options markets universa was founded in january  by cio mark spitznagel with over a decade of implementation and cumulative incremental development of its focused positive asymmetric investment approach universa has thus created an innovative investment niche and risk management methodology within an increasingly homogeneous industry universa is currently registered with the us securities and exchange commission and the us commodity futures trading commission all content   universa investments lp images and content cannot be used or reproduced without express written permission all rights reserved please see important disclosures about this website by clicking here